T1  - Learning in Networks: An Experiment on Large Networks with Real-World Features
AU  - Choi, Syngjoo
AU  - Goyal, Sanjeev
AU  - Moisan, Frederic
AU  - To, Yu Yang Tony
Y1  - 2023/02/09
PY  - 2023
