T1  - Pre-grant Patent Disclosure and Analyst Forecast Accuracy
AU  - Beyhaghi, Mehdi
AU  - Khashabi, Pooyan
AU  - Mohammadi, Ali
Y1  - 2022/04/28
PY  - 2022
DA  - 2023/05/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2022.4420
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.2022.4420
T2  - Management Science
JF  - Management Science
JO  - Management Science
